# App Configuration
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=http://localhost:3000 

# Cross-Device Meeting Configuration
# These variables enable users to join meetings from different devices
# The system uses persistent user IDs (stored in localStorage) to identify the same user across devices
# Mobile-compatible video constraints ensure connection works on tablets and smartphones
#
# For LiveKit setup:
# 1. Create a LiveKit account at https://livekit.io
# 2. Get your server URL, API Key, and API Secret from the LiveKit dashboard
# 3. Set the environment variables below
# 4. Users can now join meetings on desktop, mobile, and tablets with unified identity
